{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","titleTextRelFontSize":10,"subTitleText":"","subTitleTextRelFontSize":6,"presenterText":"","presenterTextRelFontSize":4,"dateText":"","dateTextRelFontSize":3,"logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","sectionTextRelFontSize":8,"smallerSectionText":"","smallerSectionTextRelFontSize":5},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"figure","stretch":true,"fillArea":false,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"none","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":true,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":true,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgHeight":300,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":true,"hideFigureFootnote":true,"presentationObjectInReportInfo":{"id":"c3f9ebf8-3f8a-45f9-a68d-627fb3e604e8","moduleId":"m003","isDefault":false,"selectedReplicantValue":""}}],[{"type":"text","markdown":"Between 2020 and 2023, service volumes remained consistently high, fluctuating between 167,000 and 224,000 deliveries per quarter. Notable surges were observed in Q2 2021 (224,078) and Q2 2022 (216,454), suggesting strong service performance during those periods. However, from 2024 onward, a gradual decline becomes evident, with quarterly deliveries dropping below 180,000 in several instances — the lowest being 164,774 in Q1 2025.

A moderate rebound is seen in Q2 2025 (220,173), followed by a slight decline in Q3 2025 (193,579). This rebound suggests partial recovery in service utilization after earlier declines.

Overall, while institutional delivery services have remained resilient, the data points to short-term fluctuations and a mild downward shift beginning in late 2023, highlighting the need to sustain consistent service delivery and reporting across quarters.","stretch":true,"fillArea":false,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"primary","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":false,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgHeight":300,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":false,"hideFigureFootnote":false}]],"useHeader":false,"headerText":"Yearly Trend of Institutional Delivery Service"}}

